Bio-Seq-GenomeID version 1
=============================

A universal text-based intentifier ("GenomeID") for human genomes
Bio::Seq::GenomeID - Perl extension to generate a genomeID for human genomes

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

* MIME::Base64
* Bio::DB::Sam
* List::MoreUtils
* Switch
* Math::CDF

